Create a Lightning Report or Dashboard Folder

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
Available in: Lightning Experience, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions, Enhanced Folder Sharing
NEEDED
To create report folders: Create Report Folders, To create dashboard folders: Create Dashboard Folders
On the Analytics tab, select Create | Lightning | Folder, or on the Reports or Dashboards tab, click New Folder.
Name the folder. The folder name must be unique across all report and dashboard folders.
Click Save.
title: Creating Folders for Lightning Reports and Dashboards
